## Scope

When a file contains both code and explanatory content, the code portions are covered by LICENSE-CODE and the explanatory or educational portions are covered by LICENSE-CONTENT, unless a file states otherwise.

This structure keeps the software reusable while preserving the non-commercial, share-alike terms for the educational material.
